Predicting Art Prices at Auction
The objective of this project is to use machine learning models to predict art price to discern a pattern of which factors influence art prices more because art prices at auction are extremely unstable.

League of Legends Rank Prediction
A major objective was to use neural networks such as TabTransformer to see how well it would perform on tabular data such as in predicting ranks in video games such as League of Legends.
